{"type": "article", "id": 23118, "title": "容易撞包？这些小物随时帮你换个风格", "description": "用起来！", "date": "2016-03-03T10:00:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 3786, "name": "包袋"}, {"id": 2420, "name": "手提包"}, {"id": 24270, "name": "可拆卸肩带"}, {"id": 672, "name": "丝巾"}, {"id": 17309, "name": "流苏"}, {"id": 24271, "name": "毛球"}, {"id": 325, "name": "Fendi"}, {"id": 671, "name": "Gucci"}], "category": 19, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 132, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021434357D5Xov6UdWBhic3J.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>对于很多爱美女性来说，包包可能就是她们全身上下最迷信的装饰、最治愈的礼物。但如果你同时又痛恨与别人“撞衫撞包”、热衷新鲜感（大部分人都是吧），除了不停“买买买”以外，还能有其它法子吗？<br></p>\n<p class=\"\">也许有，最近流行一些装饰包袋的方式，很简单，这里介绍点。</p>\n<h2>换肩带：</h2>\n<p class=\"\">Fendi 从 2016 年春夏的秀场，模特们就开始拿着带有花朵、蛇纹等肩带的手包出现，接着秋冬季的种类和颜色又变得更加丰富。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702143417GyDidgxOPTpaHqsh.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021434185t6q7fXbQAkyhDKE.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61111111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">这其实是 Fendi 新推出的可拆卸肩带，就叫 Strap You，素色、蛇纹、花朵、编织、拼贴“宝石”等样式应有尽有。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702143419YC2mVUG3cE0p6sMv.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702143419RgudLPhWls2HSfvE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607021434209Jx1DeFfQnGbXRPv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">虽然有时候看起来像是流浪歌手的吉他肩带，但毕竟是来自 Fendi 这样的爆款制造机，和之前的小恶魔、毛毛球系列一样迅速蹿红。在最近的时装周街拍时尚不难看到时尚达人们这样的搭配，简单又多变。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702143421VarQLSGAPjYxBMoz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65740741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702143421egKSjZnx6XRJTUNE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.81692573\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">迎接春天到来不如试试那些布满花朵的、“宝石”拼贴的，像是完全给包袋换了个风格。喜欢简洁经典就选素色，撞色的搭配和经典款的黑色包袋一块，看起来挺出彩。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702143422fJkBqOzHGwVNtrYZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75621891\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">还有 Gucci 经典的肩带设计：</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021434224ek1YWQzjiKLJnBw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">唯一（而又紧要）的问题是，有人在 Instagram 发了如下照片说：“这根带子比我的包还贵！” 是的，<a href=\"http://www.fendi.com/us/woman/strap-you/view-all.html\">Fendi 官网上有售的</a>，价格大概在 800 美元左右，对于这样的价格买一根肩带，你只能安慰自己这毕竟比 Fendi 的包便宜多了。</p>\n<p class=\"\">或者，借鉴这种思路就好。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702143423gTuKeDJ7x5mpo9La.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.684375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>毛毛球和挂饰：</h2>\n<p class=\"\">在包包上挂一个毛毛球，大概是最常见的一种方式。并且这个装饰品有越来越巨大的趋势，可能是一个迷你的包，但毛毛球要比包还大。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070214342498STJvVNcF3AotW2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.99519231\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">而这个毛茸茸的小玩意，最大的优势在于你想扮可爱没问题，如果穿一身黑什么的耍酷，用包包上这个显眼的饰品中和一下，也用不着担心看起来老气横秋。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702143425nZBPYp6AlIG4VFkM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74537037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702143425hERFaflmjeQCAZI2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.60150376\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702143426Y18eCdQBI39SNMt2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67355372\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702143426vscNz1oRpqa4SBuf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64598025\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">包袋品牌们也推出过很多各式各样的挂坠，市场上不同价位可选范围很广，也可以用来打破单调：</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702143427inlvEFq86LuhMy5x.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.4747191\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702143427eK6vYgW8R2mDzx5P.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.44990177\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>流苏：</h2>\n<p class=\"\">当然啦，这里说的流苏不是先前流行那种波西米亚风的一簇簇丝线，而最好是圆滑的皮革制成的，看起来有质感多了。比如 Sophie Hulme 推出的大眼流苏吊坠：</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702143428H5SYair1yod9QFDN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75637755\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702143428349AXayh0cl1GYSq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72705314\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021434290k6mLX3vFOuUHwib.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702143429p6m5SAnclUBN7ZzG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70277778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<h2>mini 包：</h2>\n<p class=\"\">各大品牌都争先恐后推出的极小极精致的 mini 包，俘获了不少少女的心。但因为实在是除了手机外什么也装不了，<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/12665.html\">有些人开始背两个包</a>。而 mini 包的小巧可爱，用一个来装饰大包也不错，增加层次感。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702143432IKx42anYkiF1Hbzy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.99848943\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702143432xeVL7g1hNn0JFiEZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75128999\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702143433esv36YQlyHIpn7G0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70092593\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<h2>丝巾：</h2>\n<p class=\"\">这样的搭配很多年前就有啦，系一个小蝴蝶结或是绑在把手上。只是这种方式看起来没前面几个保险，搭配不好很容易变成韩剧男主角的妈妈哟。只限于在包和丝巾本身就很好看的情况下锦上添花。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702143433ocbnu7RO8SxV165m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702143434Yag2BwceC3TxWIo6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021434348PkKhln6LYy2gt9d.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></figure>\n\n"}